== Overview ==

MoBIE (Multimodal Big Image Data Exploration) is a framework for sharing and interactive browsing of multimodal big image data. The MoBIE Fiji viewer is based on [https://imagej.net/BigDataViewer BigDataViewer] and enables the browsing of MoBIE datasets. For more information please visit the GitHub [https://github.com/mobie-org/mobie README].

== Installation ==

The MoBIE Fiji viewer can be installed by adding the MoBIE Update Site: http://sites.imagej.net/MoBIE/. For details on how to install an update site click [[Following_an_update_site|here]].

To start MoBIE in Fiji, select Plugins > MoBIE from the main menu.

